SUMMARY:Speed Puzzling Night
DESCRIPTION:Think you’re the fastest puzzler in town? 🧩 Join us for Speed Puzzling\, hosted by @portlandpuzzle starting Thursday\, October 23rd at 7PM at Hillsboro Downtown Station! Complete a 500-piece puzzle as fast as possible. ⏱️ The 1st-place winner takes home $100! \nSign up ahead of time to secure your spot — walk-ins are welcome\, but extra puzzles are limited. This competition is open to all ages\, so bring your friends\, family\, or puzzle-loving crew and see who can piece it together the fastest. 🧠✨ The cost is $35/team\, and teams tend to be about 4 people. \nSpeed Puzzling will happen every other Thursday\, so mark your calendars and get ready to puzzle for glory! \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/speed-puzzling-night-2/2026-03-26/
LOCATION:Hillsboro Downtown Station\, 320 SE Baseline St\, Hillsboro\, O\, 97123\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,Gaming,Kids Calendar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/speed-puzzling-at-hillsboro-downtown-station.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Hillsboro downtown Station":MAILTO:manager@hillsborodowntownstation.com
END:VEVENT
