SUMMARY:Tiny Tumble and Play
DESCRIPTION:Looking for a fun\, active\, and safe way to engage your toddler? Join us at Thunder Elite for Tiny Tumble and Play\, a playful open gym event specially designed for children ages 0 to 5. This is the perfect opportunity for your little one to explore movement\, build gross motor skills\, and socialize in a positive\, encouraging environment. \nYour child will have a blast exploring our bright and padded gym space\, filled with exciting age-appropriate activities such as: \n✔ Tumbling and jumping on the trampoline✔ Balancing on the low beam to build strength and focus✔ Crawling and rolling on soft\, cushioned mats✔ Climbing on toddler-safe ladders and blocks✔ Swinging on the rope ✔ Playing with toddler toys\, balls\, building blocks\, and sensory items \n​Each activity is designed to help develop coordination\, flexibility\, and confidence while encouraging curiosity and independence. Parents and caregivers are welcome to guide\, support\, and enjoy the experience right alongside their children. \n🎟 Admission is just $15 per child\, and parents attend for free. Be sure to check the event host’s website to confirm this is happening on the specific date you’re interested in!. \n📍 To keep the experience safe and enjoyable\, attendance is limited to 50 participants\, so we highly recommend pre-registering in advance. \nWhether you’re a returning family or it’s your first visit to Thunder Elite\, Tiny Tumble and Play is a wonderful way to create joyful memories with your little one while introducing them to movement and physical activity in a supportive gym environment. \n👉 Reserve your spot today using the registration link below!
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/tiny-tumble-and-play/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Thunder Elite’s Tumble and Learn Preschool\, 12900 Se HWY 212\, Clackamas\, OR\, 97015\, United States
CATEGORIES:Kids Calendar,Playgroup,Sports
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/284849577_10159017698540888_8757093534903939095_n.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Tumble and Learn Preschool":MAILTO:jaylyn@thunderelite.com
END:VEVENT
