SUMMARY:Impact NW Community Playgroup
DESCRIPTION:🌟Join Us for our Community Playgroup at Brentwood Darlington Community Center!🌟 \nWe are excited to invite families to fill out the form if they are interested in attending our Community Playgroup. This fun and engaging program is designed to encourage positive interactions between parents and children in a welcoming environment. \n✅ How to Sign Up: Please complete the form to express your interest. Upon receiving your response\, we will contact you to confirm your attendance. \n⚠️ Limited Capacity: Please note that the playgroup classroom has a limited capacity. Once we reach this limit\, we will no longer be able to accept additional responses or participants. \n🌱 Playgroup Sessions: The playgroup will be held on the 2nd and 4th Friday of the month\, and we are committed to being equitable in offering this opportunity to all families who are interested. \nWe look forward to seeing you and your little one at the Brentwood Darlington Community Center! ✨
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/impact-nw-community-playgroup-3/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Brentwood-Darlington Community Center\, 7211 SE 62nd Ave\, Portland\, O\, 97206\, United States
CATEGORIES:Playgroup
