SUMMARY:Scat | The Doo-Doo Diaries
DESCRIPTION:Are you feces fanatic? A turd nerd? Or do you just want to know what you stepped in? Join us for a down-and-dirty look at how scat influences life in the Tillamook State Forest\, and you’ll soon be the number one expert on number two! \nProgram times:   \nMar 27\, 2026\, 11:30 AM – 12:00 PM \nMar 28\, 2026\, 1:30 PM – 2:00 PM \nMar 29\, 2026\, 11:30 AM – 12:00 PM \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
